    "direct_runtime_supported": false,
    "support_class_after": "broker/coordinator-only",
    "blocker_bead_id": "asupersync-9r5lmo",
    "blocked_reason": "ServiceWorkerGlobalScope can be terminated between lifecycle events, so a direct BrowserRuntime lane needs a dedicated lifetime and region-ownership contract before it can preserve asupersync cancellation, drain/finalize, and replay invariants. The shipped user path remains bounded broker registration plus durable handoff to dedicated-worker or browser-main direct-runtime lanes."
  },
